1. Molim vas, da li imate važeći *pasoš*? (Excuse me, do you have a valid passport?)
2. Oni su izgubili svoje *pasoše* na aerodromu. (They lost their passports at the airport.)
3. U redu za pasošku kontrolu je bio veoma dug. (The line for passport control was very long.)
4. Moramo produžiti važenje naših *pasoša*. (We need to extend the validity of our passports.)
5. Kada putujete u inostranstvo, uvek nosite svoj *pasoš* sa sobom. (When traveling abroad, always carry your passport with you.)
6. Policija je zatražila da pokažem svoj *pasoš* kao identifikaciju. (The police asked me to show my passport as identification.)
7. Nisam mogao da nađem svoj *pasoš* danima. (I couldn't find my passport for days.)
8. Država je uvela nove mere za izdavanje *pasoša*. (The state has introduced new measures for issuing passports.)
9. Zbog oštećenja, moj *pasoš* nije mogao biti pročitan na aerodromu. (Due to damage, my passport could not be read at the airport.)
10. Ukoliko ne posedujete *pasoš*, nećete moći da putujete van zemlje. (If you don't have a passport, you won't be able to travel outside the country.)